70
00:03:59,719 --> 00:04:00,439
Don't spill it!

71
00:04:00,520 --> 00:04:01,759
Chug, chug, chug!

72
00:04:05,800 --> 00:04:07,000
Oh, and Mr. Zhu said

73
00:04:07,000 --> 00:04:07,840
your grades
are in the toilet.

74
00:04:09,000 --> 00:04:09,719
What's the deal?

75
00:04:12,039 --> 00:04:13,240
I don't...

76
00:04:13,680 --> 00:04:14,919
Son, I'm not trying

77
00:04:15,639 --> 00:04:16,839
to ride you,

78
00:04:17,519 --> 00:04:19,199
but college exams are next year.

79
00:04:20,399 --> 00:04:21,839
If you keep failing,

80
00:04:22,240 --> 00:04:23,279
you're not getting

81
